Abylix Studio Privacy Policy

Last Updated :  8/11/2025 

1 - Introduction
Abylix Studio is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our products and services. By using our services, you consent to the collection and use of your data as outlined in this policy.

2 - Information We Collect
We may collect personal information such as:

Your name, email address, and contact details.

Information about your device, usage data, and service preferences.

This information is collected to provide, improve, and personalize your experience with our services.

3 - How We Use Your Information
We use the collected information to:

Provide customer support.

Improve and personalize our services and products.

Process transactions and manage your account.

We may also send you communications related to our services, such as updates, offers, and promotions, which you can opt out of at any time.

4 - Data Protection and Security
We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. However, please note that no method of electronic transmission is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

5 - Sharing Your Information
We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share information with trusted partners who help us operate our services, such as payment processors, but they are required to keep your information confidential.

We may also share your data when required by law or in response to legal processes.

6 - Cookies and Tracking Technologies
We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to improve your experience with our website and services. These technologies help us remember your preferences and provide relevant content.

You can control the use of cookies through your browser settings.

7 - Your Rights
You have the right to:

Access the personal data we hold about you.

Request corrections or deletions of your personal data.

Opt out of receiving promotional communications.

If you wish to exercise any of these rights, please contact us directly.

8 - Changes to This Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with the updated effective date.

By continuing to use our services after changes are made, you agree to the updated Privacy Policy.
